## Write a program to convert days to weeks

1 week = 7 days

```txt
Input  : 35
Output : 5
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-days-to-weeks" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){
    int days, weeks, remainder;

    printf("Enter the number of days    :   ");
    scanf("%d", &days);

    weeks = days / 7;
    remainder = days % 7;


    if (remainder == 0){
        printf("Weeks   :   %d", weeks);
    }
    else {
         printf("Weeks  :   %d      Days    :   %d", weeks, remainder );
    }
    return 0;
}
```

